'''热熔胶'''一种可塑性的固体状[[粘合剂|粘合剂]]<ref>{{cite journal|author1=王淮珠|title=浅谈EVA热熔胶及其使用|journal=印刷技术|date=2003|issue=28|url=http://d.wanfangdata.com.cn/Periodical/yinsjs200328003}}</ref>，以热塑性[[树脂|树脂]]为主要成分，添加增塑剂、增粘树脂、抗氧剂、阻燃剂及填料等成分<ref>{{cite web|author1=胡工|title=热熔胶膜配方分析|url=http://www.hechuanchem.com/ProductView.asp?ID=94|website=苏州禾川化学技术服务有限公司|accessdate=2017-04-09|date=2012-09-19|archive-date=2018-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023120407/http://www.hechuanchem.com/ProductView.asp?ID=94|dead-url=no}}</ref>，经熔融混合制成，具有无毒、无溶剂，运输、存储方便，黏合速度快、强度大等优点<ref>{{cite web|title=国内热熔胶的现状与发展|url=http://www.sszfc.com/news-6.htm|website=深圳市辉铭达科技有限公司|accessdate=2017-04-09|archive-date=2019-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190320092539/http://www.sszfc.com/news-6.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，热熔胶产量约占胶粘剂总产量的 40%。<ref>{{cite web|author1=林中祥胶粘剂技术信息网|title=热熔胶行业现状市场及未来市场分析|url=http://www.adhesive-lin.com/html/xzpd/cztt/cs/37944.html|website=南京爱德福信息科技有限公司|accessdate=2017-04-09|date=2016-08-02|archive-date=2017-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107025708/http://adhesive-lin.com/html/xzpd/cztt/cs/37944.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==特性==
与[[糨糊|糨糊]]、[[聚醋酸乙烯酯|聚醋酸乙烯酯]]（PVAC）等冷性胶相比，热熔胶在常温下为固体，加热到一定温度时熔融成为[[流体|流体]]黏合剂，脱离加热装置后，会迅速冷却固化，黏合速度快。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Gierenz|first1=Gerhard|last2=Karmann|first2=Werner|title=Adhesives and Adhesive Tapes|date=2001|publisher=John Wiley & Sons}}</ref>热熔胶通常为无色透明或半透明，棕褐色或彩色的热熔胶可能会降低粘性<ref>{{cite web|author1=Pierce Covert|title=Color and Clarity of Hot Melt Adhesives|url=http://www.woodweb.com/knowledge_base/Color_and_Clarity_of_Hot_Melt_Adhesives.html|website=WOODWEB, Inc.|publisher=Glue Machinery Corporation|accessdate=2017-04-10|date=2006-09-13|archive-date=2020-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114115717/http://www.woodweb.com/knowledge_base/Color_and_Clarity_of_Hot_Melt_Adhesives.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。热熔胶通常有棒状、颗粒状和薄膜状<ref>{{cite web|title=Adhesives and Sealants 101: Hot Melts|url=http://www.adhesivesmag.com/articles/87415-adhesives-and-sealants-101-hot-melts|website=Adhesives & Sealants Industry|accessdate=2017-04-10|date=2008-10-01|archive-date=2021-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419204742/https://www.adhesivesmag.com/articles/87415-adhesives-and-sealants-101-hot-melts|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==分类==
传统型热熔胶使用的基本树脂有[[聚氨酯|聚氨酯]]（PU）、[[聚酰胺|聚酰胺]]（PA）<ref>{{cite journal|author1=陈续明|author2=贾兰琴|author3=李瑞霞|author4=黄燕萍|coauthors=宁家成|title=用于热熔胶的聚酰胺树脂合成组成与性能关系的研究|journal=中国胶粘剂|date=2001|issue=1|pages=7-10|url=http://www.cqvip.com/qk/92184a/200101/5019870.html|access-date=2017-04-10|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612201613/http://www.cqvip.com/qk/92184a/200101/5019870.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[聚乙烯|聚乙烯]]（PE）、[[乙烯/醋酸乙烯酯共聚物|乙烯／醋酸乙烯]]（EVA）等多个品种；可生物降解型的热熔胶则可分为聚乳酸型、聚酯酰胺型、聚羟基烷酸酯型和天然高分子型等。<ref>{{cite journal|author1=郭静|author2=相恒学|author3=王倩倩|coauthors=管福成|title=热熔胶研究进展|journal=中国胶粘剂|date=2010|issue=7|pages=54-58|url=http://www.cqvip.com/qk/92184a/201007/34705126.html|access-date=2017-04-10|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610011849/http://www.cqvip.com/qk/92184a/201007/34705126.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author1=Edward Petrie|title=Synthetically Designed Hot Melt Adhesives – Polyamides and Polyesters|url=http://adhesives.specialchem.com/tech-library/article/synthetically-designed-hot-melt-adhesives-polyamides-and-polyesters?id=2035|website=SpecialChem|accessdate=2017-04-09|date=2007-10-10|archive-date=2016-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807041610/http://adhesives.specialchem.com/tech-library/article/synthetically-designed-hot-melt-adhesives-polyamides-and-polyesters?id=2035|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*PA热熔胶以[[聚酰胺|聚酰胺]]为主要原料，对纺织品、纤维的粘接牢度非常强，耐水洗，广泛应用于服装粘合衬行业。<ref>{{cite journal|author1=田家强|coauthors=叶庆国|title=四元共聚酰胺热熔胶的研制|journal=中国胶粘剂|date=2003|issue=5|pages=35-37|url=http://www.cqvip.com/qk/92184a/2003005/8430252.html|accessdate=2017-04-10|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613164826/http://www.cqvip.com/qk/92184a/2003005/8430252.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author1=田家强|coauthors=叶庆国|title=新型聚酰胺热熔胶的研制与开发|journal=中国胶粘剂|date=2004|issue=4|pages=29-31|url=http://www.cqvip.com/qk/92184a/200404/10358385.html|accessdate=2017-04-10|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613164829/http://www.cqvip.com/qk/92184a/200404/10358385.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=PA热熔胶膜-共聚酰胺热熔胶膜|url=http://www.sujucn.com/cn/product/PA.html|website=苏州塑聚材料科技有限公司|accessdate=2017-04-10|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319091731/http://sujucn.com/cn/product/PA.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*PES热熔胶采用低分子量聚乙烯作树脂原料<ref>{{cite web|title=聚乙烯热熔胶黏剂简介|url=http://www.evapowder.cn/2011-02-12-03-21-56/35-2010-11-25-01-37-59/151-2011-02-25-02-31-51.html|website=江阴市理想橡塑科技有限公司|accessdate=2017-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170410213831/http://www.evapowder.cn/2011-02-12-03-21-56/35-2010-11-25-01-37-59/151-2011-02-25-02-31-51.html|archive-date=2017-04-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，价格低，主要应用于纸箱包装、地毯拼缝、汽车地毯衬背、服装衬布粘接等方面<ref>{{cite web|title=Ethylene Copolymers in Hot melt applications|url=http://adhesives.specialchem.com/selection-guide/ethylene-copolymers-for-adhesives-and-sealants/hot-melt-applications?id=hotmelt|website=SpecialChem|accessdate=2017-04-10|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610131833/https://adhesives.specialchem.com/selection-guide/ethylene-copolymers-for-adhesives-and-sealants/hot-melt-applications?id=hotmelt|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*EVA热熔胶（英文：Ethylene Viny Acetate）是由[[乙烯|乙烯]]（E）及乙烯基[[醋酸盐|醋酸盐]]（VA）共聚而成。乙烯基醋酸盐（VA content）的含量越高，其透明度、柔软度及坚韧度越高。<ref>{{cite journal|author1=M. NARDIN|author2=M. BROGLY|coauthors=J. SCHULTZ|title=Effects of the composition of hot-melt adhesives on their bulk and interfacial properties|journal=JOURNAL DE PHYSIQUE IV|date=1993|volume=3|url=https://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/file/index/docid/251872/filename/ajp-jp4199303C7235.pdf|access-date=2017-04-10|archive-date=2019-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191025002547/https://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/file/index/docid/251872/filename/ajp-jp4199303C7235.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==应用==
